snippet.title: EA SPORTS 2014 FIFA World Cup - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Official gameplay trailer for EA SPORTS 2014 FIFA World Cup. Learn more: http://bit.ly/1nx6SDj
NA pre-order: http://o.ea.com/19694 | UK: http://bit.ly/PHLKeJ 

'The World Is Ours' by David Correy is the official Coca-Cola anthem of their World Cup 2014 campaign.

Launches in North America on April 15, 2014, Europe on April 17, 2014.
